 PA^2 = PB^2  \\ \Rightarrow (x+1)^2 + (y-4)^2 = (x-3)^2 + (y+2)^2 \\ \Rightarrow  x^2 +2x + 1 + y^2 -8y +16 = x^2 -6x +9 +y^2 + 4y + 4 \\ \Rightarrow 2x - 8y +17 = -6x +4y +13 \\ \Rightarrow 8x - 12y + 4 = 0 \\ \Rightarrow 2x -3y + 1 = 0 
